quran[9{c,v,t}:
6,36,"dawat haq par labaik wohi log kehte hain jo suneney walay hain, rahay murdy, to inhen to Allah bas qabron hi se uthaye ga aur phir woh ( is ki adalat mein paish honay ke liye ) wapas laaye jayen ge"
6,37,"yeh log kehte hain ke iss nabi par is ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nahi utri? kaho, Allah nishani utaarnay ki poori qudrat rakhta hai, magar un mein se aksar log nadani mein mubtala hain"
6,38,"zameen mein chalne walay kisi janwar aur howa mein paron se urrnay walay kisi parinday ko dekh lau, yeh sab tumhari hi terhan ki anwaa hain, hum ne un ki taqdeer ke noshte mein koi kasar nahi choari hai, phir yeh sab apne rab ki taraf samete jatay hain"
6,39,"magar jo log hamari nshanyon ko jutlatay hain woh behray aur gungay hain, tarikeon mein parre hue hain Allah jisay chahta hai bhatka deta hai aur jisay chahta hai seedhay raste par laga deta hai"
6,40,"un se kaho, zara ghhor kar ke batao, agar kabhi tum par Allah ki taraf se koi barri museebat aa jati hai ya aakhri gharri aa pahunchti hai to kya is waqt tum Allah ke siwa kisi aur ko pkarte ho? balow agar tum sachey ho"
6,41,"a seen waqt tum Allah hi ko pkarte ho, phir agar woh chahta hai to is museebat ko tum par se taall deta hai aisay moqaon par tum apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko bhool jatay ho"
6,42,tum se pehlay bohat si qomon ki taraf hum ne rasool beje aur unn qomon ko masaaib o alaam mein mubtala kya taakay woh aajzi ke sath hamaray samnay jhuk jayen
6,43,pas jab hamari taraf se un par sakhti aayi to kyun nah unhon ne aajzi ikhtiyar ki? magar un ke dil to aur sakht hogaye aur shetan ne un ko itminan dilaya ke jo kuch tum kar rahay ho khoob kar rahay ho
6,44,"phir jab unhon ne is nasiyaat ko, jo inhen ki gayi thi, bhala diya to hum ne har terhan ki khushaaliyon ke darwazay un ke liye khol diye, yahan taq ke jab woh unn bakhshishon mein jo inhen ataa ki gayi theen khoob magan hogaye to achanak hum ne inhen pakar liya aur ab haal yeh tha ke woh har kher se mayoos thay"
